         <abstract id="aspace_dfea661dd35523321cbe033605a76294">Printed patents, reports and related material on his system for the radio control of torpedoes, inventions for musical instruments and scrapbooks of newspaper clippings and congressional publications about Hammond and his work. Half the collection is made up of clippings.</abstract>
